<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:TET%D0%AFIS_The_Soviet_Mind_Game.png" class="image" title="Screenshot of the NES version of TETЯIS: The Soviet Mind Game"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/08/TET%D0%AFIS_The_Soviet_Mind_Game.png/250px-TET%D0%AFIS_The_Soviet_Mind_Game.png" width="250" height="187" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
